        <item>
            <title>Google Photos 新增 AI 编辑标签　能够辨识 AI 生成影像</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/google-photos-will-soon-show-you-if-an-image-was-edited-with-ai/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-photos-will-soon-show-you-if-an-image-was-edited-with-ai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/google-photos-will-soon-show-you-if-an-image-was-edited-with-ai/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 11:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google photo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google photos]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271463</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著 AI 生成技术日益像真，用户愈来愈难分辨相片真伪。为提升用户对照片编辑和管理的控制，Google Photos 最近宣布下周起加入 AI 编辑照片标签功能，让用户能更简单有效地优化拍摄效果。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025132312-534x580.jpg" alt="" width="534" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025132312-534x580.jpg 534w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241025132312.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 534px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://support.google.com/photos/thread/303743987/find-out-if-your-photos-have-been-edited-with-ai?hl=en">Google</a></p><p>Google Photos 最新的 AI 标签功能让用户能一目了然地知道照片是否经过 AI 编辑处理。当用户使用 Magic Editor、Magic Eraser、Zoom Improve 或其他生成式 AI 工具编辑相片时，系统会自动在图片上添加标签，标明照片经过 AI 修改，让用户更轻松管理照片，能清楚区分哪些照片经由 AI 修改。</p><p>Google 表示这项新功能仍在测试阶段，未来会继续收集用家意见，以提升 AI 编辑透明度。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://support.google.com/photos/thread/303743987/find-out-if-your-photos-have-been-edited-with-ai?hl=en">Google</a>、<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/24/24278663/google-photos-generative-ai-label-reimagine-best-take">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/apple-ai-clean-up-ios-18-1-beta-3/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 18.1 AI 一键清相片路人杂物　旅游景点不再人头涌涌</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/white-house-presses-govt-ai-use-with-eye-on-security-guardrails/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">拜登公布 AI 加强国家安全计划　必须超越竞争对手如中国 + 强调安全性</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/google-photos-will-soon-show-you-if-an-image-was-edited-with-ai/ai/">Google Photos 新增 AI 编辑标签　能够辨识 AI 生成影像</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
