        <item>
            <title>保时捷 Macan + Taycan 纯电双雄抵港　最高 784 km 续航 + 零百最快 2.4 秒</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/porsche-macan-taycan/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=porsche-macan-taycan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/porsche-macan-taycan/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:30:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Porsche Macan]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Porsche Taycan]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[保时捷]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271492</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>纯电潮流席卷全城，Porsche 近日正式在香港推出纯电动 SUV Macan 及新款 Taycan。适逢车系抵港，Porsche 特别于香港 ELEMENTS 圆方举行一连四日 （10 月 24 日 – 27 日） 的「保时捷圆方车展」，现在就让小编带大家看看 Porsche 这两款新车吧。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_110548-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_110548-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_110548-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Taycan（左）；Macan（右）</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kv_3newmodels-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kv_3newmodels-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kv_3newmodels-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Porsche Macan</h2><p>全新纯电动 Macan 结合了优雅与运动感，配合最新推出的 Provence 车身颜色更突显其精致动感的美学。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-6-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲流线型 Coupé 设计</p><p>Macan 采用流线型 Coupé 设计，另外配备了保时捷主动式空气力学套件 (PAA)，并结合扰流装置，使车辆的风阻系数低至 0.25。搭配扁平的头灯组件及四点式日行灯，整体车身比例锐利且充满张力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲四点式日行灯</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271503" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲扁平头灯组件</p><p>车尾部分的设计更进一步体现了 Macan 的运动感。标志性的保时捷流线型车顶线条流畅，无缝连接至车尾的平整后窗，完美呼应了无边框车门和独特的侧裙设计，令整体外观更加一体化且具现代感。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112339-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112339-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112339-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车尾的轮廓分明，尤其是「车肩」设计，强调出充满力量感的造型。车尾灯中央嵌入如雕塑般的保时捷徽标，不仅增添现代美学，更成为了整体设计中的点睛之笔。这些细节让 Macan 外观既时尚前衞又不失豪华。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-5-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-5-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>纯电动 Macan 搭载了容量达 100 kWh 的新一代电池，单次充电即可提供高达 784 km 的城市续航距离（WLTP ），能满足日常通勤需求之余，也使长距离旅程更为便捷之余成为同级车型中出色的长途续航之选。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112322-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112322-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112322-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112410-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112410-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112410-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>性能方面，Macan 前后轴配备了先进的 PSM（Porsche Stability Management）系统，输出功率高达 470 kW，并产生高达 1,130 Nm 的扭力，让 Macan 能够轻松驾驭各种路面条件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Macan 另外设有双阀门技术的 PASM（Porsche Active Suspension Management） 主动式悬载调整系统，该系统能即时调节车身的悬载高度和刚性，确保转弯和高速驾驶时稳定舒适。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewallelectricmac-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>动力系统的核心为最新的 800 V 电压高压电池系统，这一系统作为 PPE（Premium Platform Electric） 平台的核心零件，支援高达 270 kW 的充电功率，让 Macan 在快速充电站仅需约 21 分钟，即可将电量从 10% 充至 80%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112513-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112513-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112513-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Porsche Taycan</h2><p>新款 Taycan 延续了保时捷电动车的卓越设计理念，著重展现其宽阔而强势的外观造型，并将运动感与豪华感完美结合。车头设计上，新款 Taycan 采用了保时捷标志性的四点式 LED 矩阵头灯，让车头视觉效果更具辨识度，同时提供清晰而精致的照明体验。这款头灯设计提升了车辆的辨识度，更让其夜间造型更为出众。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan5-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan5-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲采用了保时捷标志性的四点式 LED 矩阵头灯</p><p>Taycan 的尾部设计同样细腻，尾灯组件采用了立体玻璃质感，并在灯条内嵌入了发光的保时捷标志。这款灯条在进入或离开车辆时会显示带有迎宾动画的效果，不仅提升了车辆的科技感，也让 Taycan 在驻车或行驶中均成为众人目光的焦点。此外，夺目的 Turbonite 配色能更好地区分 Turbo 和 Turbo S 车型，增强了这些高性能车型的识别度及独特魅力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112207-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112207-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241024_112207-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271508" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲灯条在进入或离开车辆时会显示带有迎宾动画的效果</p><p>动力表现方面，新款 Taycan 提供了极佳的加速和续航能力。Taycan 基本款仅需 4.8 秒，即可从静止加速至 100 km/h，而 Turbo S 更仅需 2.4 秒，在性能上相较前代车型有显著提升。此外，新增的 Push-to-Pass 一键加速功能可在短短 10 秒，内额外提供 70 kW 的动力，让驾驶者随时享受强劲推进的快感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在续航方面，新款 Taycan 经过改良的 800 V 直流充电系统支援高达 320 kW 的充电功率，相较前代提升了 50 kW，且充电效率大幅增强。仅需 18 分钟，即可将电量从 10% 充至 80%，缩短充电时间提升了长途旅行的便利性，确保车主随时保持最佳续航状态。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1271511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/thenewtaycan4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新纯电动 Macan 现已接受订购*，售价：</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 72px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Macan 4 Electric</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港币 $1,048,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Macan 4S Electric</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港币 $1,198,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Macan Turbo Electric</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港币 $1,448,000 起*</td></tr></tbody></table><p>*制造商的建议零售价（包括首次登记税）只供参考，不包括运输费、保险费、道路许可证、选择性或区域性设备。</p><p>新款 Taycan 现已接受订购*，售价：</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 72px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Taycan</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港币 $1,478,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Taycan 4S</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港币 $1,888,000 起*</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Taycan Turbo</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港币 $3,368,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo GT</td><td style="width: 50%;">港币 $3,878,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo GT with Weissach Package</td><td style="width: 50%;">港币 $3,878,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan 4 Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港币 $1,638,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan 4S Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港币 $1,978,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港币 $2,818,000 起*</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;">Taycan Turbo S Cross Turismo</td><td style="width: 50%;">港币 $3,388,000 起*</td></tr></tbody></table><p>*制造商的建议零售价（包括首次登记税）只供参考，不包括运输费、保险费、道路许可证、选择性或区域性设备。</p><p>「保时捷圆方车展」详情：<br />
日期： 10 月 24 &#8211; 27 日<br />
时间：上午 11 时至下午 7 时<br />
地点：香港九龙 ELEMENTS 圆方 1 楼金区展览场地</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/porsche-macanev-800v/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新 Porsche 电动 Macan 香港预览   800V 架构快速充电 + 可配气压避震及后轮转向</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/porsche-macan-taycan/life-tech/auto/">保时捷 Macan + Taycan 纯电双雄抵港　最高 784 km 续航 + 零百最快 2.4 秒</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
