        <item>
            <title>Apple 将发表 M4 Mac 产品 　外媒预计：MacBook Pro + Mac Mini + iMac</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/apple-teases-week-of-mac-announcements-starting-on-monday/software/mac-os-x/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-teases-week-of-mac-announcements-starting-on-monday</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/apple-teases-week-of-mac-announcements-starting-on-monday/software/mac-os-x/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 06:00:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac OS X]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple M4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple M4 MacBook Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple MacBook]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1271450</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 全球市场推广副总裁 Greg Joswiak 今日在 X （前称 Twitter）发文透露，Apple 将会在下周一起推出新 Mac 。综合外媒消息，这次将会推出多款采用最新 M4 晶片的 Mac 电脑，其中包括早前我们报道过，本月初已经有俄罗斯 YouTuber 抢先开箱（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/07/m4-macbook-pro-from-russian-youtube-channel/software/mac-os-x/">相关报道</a>），传闻标准配置达 16GB RAM 的 M4 MacBook Pro（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/m4-macbook-pro-allegedly-leaked-configurations-show-up/software/mac-os-x/">相关报道</a>）。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Mac (😉) your calendars! We have an exciting week of announcements ahead, starting on Monday morning. Stay tuned… <a href="https://t.co/YnoCYkZq6c">pic.twitter.com/YnoCYkZq6c</a></p><p>— Greg Joswiak (@gregjoz) <a href="https://twitter.com/gregjoz/status/1849484363165213148?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 24, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>知名 Apple 爆料人 Mark Gurman 亦在 X 发文，表示 Apple 将会在 10 月 30 日在美国洛杉矶举办线上发布会，据悉今次将不会以 Keynote 形式发布新 Mac，因为 Apple 分开了不同预约时间段邀请各大媒体人。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Apple is inviting media/creators at different appointment times throughout the day on 10/30 in my town of LA — they seemingly aren’t bringing a group together to watch a keynote video. So the announcement is online only (video and press releases), as I’ve been indicating. <a href="https://t.co/sVk6GjrVeC">https://t.co/sVk6GjrVeC</a></p><p>— Mark Gurman (@markgurman) <a href="https://twitter.com/markgurman/status/1848764913923330064?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 22, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>除了 MacBook Pro，《MacRumors》指出，这次亦会发布全新 iMac 及 Mac mini。预料高阶版本的 MacBook Pro 将搭载 M4 Pro 及 M4 Max 晶片。市场分析指出，Apple 选择在 10 月底推出新产品，目的是抢占年末的消费旺季，并透过更强大产品阵容，吸引专业用户和创意产业消费者。M 系列晶片推出以来，效能和电池续航力均获广泛好评，这次发布的 M4 系列晶片 Mac 有望可再提升续航力及效能。去年 Apple 亦在 10 月举办「Scary Fast」发布会，推出采用全新 M3 晶片的 iMac。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/10/24/apple-is-readied-for-an-entire-week-of-m4-mac-announcements">Apple Insider</a>、<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/24/apple-m4-announcements-next-week/">MacRumors</a>、<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/24/24266448/apple-mac-announcements-october-2024">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://tomsguide.com/computing/macbooks/apple-m4-mac-launch-date-just-leaked-heres-when-to-expect-the-annoucement">Tom&#8217;s Guid</a>e、<a href="https://www.theshortcut.com/p/apple-mac-m4-announcements-teaser">Shortcut</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/apple-m4-mac/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple M4 Mac 或于 11 月推出，料全面取消 USB-A 接口</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/apple-teases-week-of-mac-announcements-starting-on-monday/software/mac-os-x/">Apple 将发表 M4 Mac 产品 　外媒预计：MacBook Pro + Mac Mini + iMac</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
